	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MISC CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Change Custom 1 -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>At the title screen Hold L1 + R1 + Select + Triangle.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Change Custom 2 -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>At the title screen hold L1 + R1 + Select + Square.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Infinite Spell Power -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>At the title screen hold L1 + L2 + R1 + R2.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; School Uniform -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>At the title screen hold L1 + Select + Triangle + R2 + Start.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Sound Test -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>At the title screen press Left, Circle, Down, Triangle, Right, Square, up, X, L1, R2, L2, R1 + Start.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Character Biographies -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>Unlock all thirteen endings, then select Pamphlet mode. A new Guide option will be available.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Time Attack and Score Attack Modes -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>Beat the game with an ''A'' ending to access the ''???'' option in the pamphlet menu. This reveals a new ''Extra Mode'', which contains selections for ''Time Attack'' and ''Score Attack'' mini-games.</font>&nbsp;<br>
          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">ACTION REPLAY CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Joker Command -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>D0067EE4 0000</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Infinite HP -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>800730F8 0003</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; All endings & Extra Mode -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>80071728 FFFF</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Infinite time -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>80073128 0FB8<br>80073134 0000</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Have all hints -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>8007172A 00FF</font>&nbsp;<br><br>
	 </tr>
	</table>
